      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STROP (3) was out of the placings last time when eighth at Sale (29.85) but scored five back at this track (28.42). Solid record here at the distance winning two races. Should bounce back. SIMPLY NED (1) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Kraken Babe (24.32) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Leading player again. PRAWN AND ORDER (4) has been in the frame at her last two runs, most recently when third (24.66) in a Grade 5 over 425m at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. MIDNIGHT THUNDER (8) was strongly fancied last time but finished second (25.93), beaten 1.3 lengths. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Well placed and gets his chance.",
